<span class="line"></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h3 id="interface-接口" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#interface-接口" aria-hidden="true">#</a> interface 接口</h3>
